snippet.title: Living like a Real life BARBIE for 24 Hours!! *Funny Public Reaction*
snippet.description:
In today's exciting video, I'm taking on the ultimate challenge: living like Barbie for an entire day! From her iconic fashion choices to her glamorous lifestyle, I'll be immersing myself in everything Barbie. Get ready to join me on this fun and fabulous adventure as I embrace pink, glitter, and all things Barbie. About MalaimurasuNews TV

Malaimurasu TV (Tamil: மாலைமுரசு ) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on Jun 09, 2016. Due to its independent editorial stance it became extremely popular in India and abroad within days of its launch and continues to remain so till date.The channel looks at issues through the eyes of the common man and serves as a platform that airs people's views.The editorial policy is built on strong ethics and fair reporting methods that does not favour or oppose any individual, ideology, group, government, organisation or sponsor.The channel’s primary aim is taking unbiased and accurate information to the socially conscious common man.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu ||Something Missamma Episode 06 || Pre Wedding || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Episode 06 Pre Wedding MCM
Filmymoji releases its new episode of Missamma series where Middle class Madhu will be forced to assist Penta Reddy in chopping someone’s hand off. Meanwhile Dupesh lands in jammalamadugu and proposes to take a pre-wedding shoot of bulli Guvva and Sravani. The broker introduces the alliance as a Dubai return and Madhu blackmails him for money for not revealing this narrative. Dupesh takes out bride and the groom along with MCM and Komali for the pre-wedding shoot and instead of taking pictures he convinces bulli Guvva to click his pictures with the bride. Watch the full episode to find out the shocking truth which Dupesh reveals about the marriage and whether NaatuGuntala gang finds out about the whereabouts of Madhu.

snippet.title: Madhavi ने Bhide को चाय नहीं अचार बनाने का दिया Order |Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah|Unknown Guest
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Madhavi and Bhide are in a hurry to pack pickles and papads for their customers. Bhide is waiting for tea but Madhavi explains to him about urgent delivery. Bhide calls Madhavi a home minister then Madhavi orders him to focus on pickles and Papad not on the tea. Stay tuned for more. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 2726
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal #shahrukh_khan #kajol #shahrukh 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Unknown Guest:

snippet.title: Iconic scene from Thimiru movie | Vishal | Reema Sen | Sriya Reddy | Sun NXT
snippet.description:
In this super hit scene from "Thimiru," Shriya Reddy is an arrogant moneylender exploiting families unable to repay loans. Vishal helps Reema Sen's family and rejects Shriya's proposal. She kidnaps Vishal's parents, leading to her own downfall as Vishal get into Action. Watch the full movie on Sun NXT.

Watch Full Movie on SUN NXT - https://bit.ly/3s0mS9e

Thimiru  is a 2006 Indian Tamil-language action film written and directed by Tarun Gopi in his directorial debut. It stars Vishal, Reema Sen, Sriya Reddy, I. M. Vijayan, Manoj K. Jayan and Vadivelu, while Kiran Rathod makes a cameo appearance. The film's score and soundtrack are composed by Yuvan Shankar Raja. Produced by Vikram Krishna, under the banner of G K Film Corporation, Thimiru was released on 4 August 2006 and became one of the top-grossing Tamil films in 2006.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Mega Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 13th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Sirf Tum Mega Episode 30 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 13th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3848: Time Par Order Ready
--------------------------------------------------------
Madhavi has received a big order of tomato pickles to be delivered, but the cylinder at Bhide's house goes out of gas. Tapu Sena assists Bhide in getting a new cylinder from Jetha's place, Tapu Sena brings the cylinder to Bhide's place. Madhavi successfully cooks and prepares the pickle order and packs it for the customer. Later, the customer being grateful for the order asks Madhavi to charge him as per the current price of the tomatoes. Watch the episode to know more.  

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3848, 12 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Episode 32 Teaser - 13th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Written by: Seema Munaf
Directed by: Mazhar Moin
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Jiya Shankar admits feelings for Abhishek Malhan, slams Pooja Bhatt; says Elvish has a heart of gold
snippet.description:
Jiya Shankar, who recently got eliminated from Bigg Boss OTT season 2 and couldn't be a part of Top 5 spoke to ETimes TV about her journey in the show. She shared that she would not like to meet Jad Hadid and Avinash Sachdev after the show and also revealed the reason behind the same. Reacting to her fight with Pooja Bhatt, Jiya slammed the Dil Hai Ke Maanta Nahin actress for saying that she won't get work in the industry. She further spoke about her special bond with Abhishek Malhan and admitted to having feelings for him and a special place in her heart. Jiya got emotional talking about Abhishek Malhan's close ones commenting on her character but also shared that if Abhishek is willing she would take their bond ahead. She also opened up about her equation with her father and why she would never go back to him.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:

All the gents of Gokuldham society have gathered at Abdul's shop to drink soda. They have a very light hearted conversation on the on a very interesting topic. The next day, Rita comes and announces the result of the audition which Tapu Sena had given. But to their surprise, Gogi is not selected for the ad shoot. This disappoints everyone in society. Stay tuned to get your daily dose of laughter.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 261
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.title: 12th Fail Official Teaser | Vidhu Vinod Chopra | Vikrant Massey | 27th October 2023
snippet.description:
प्रिय विद्यार्थी,

आपको ध्यान होगा कि करीब 4 साल पहले दृष्टि संस्थान के पूर्व विद्यार्थी मनोज कुमार शर्मा (IPS) के तैयारी के दिनों से जुड़े संघर्षों पर 'ट्वेल्थ फेल' नामक उपन्यास प्रकाशित हुआ था। इसमें दृष्टि की ही विद्यार्थी श्रद्धा जोशी (IRS) की कहानी भी थी जो मनोज की जीवनसंगिनी हैं। उपन्यास दृष्टि के ही पूर्व विद्यार्थी अनुराग पाठक (जॉइंट कमिश्नर, GST) ने लिखा था और भूमिका लिखी थी विकास सर ने!

अब इसी उपन्यास पर 27 अक्तूबर को एक बड़ी फिल्म आ रही है जिसके लेखक, निर्माता और निर्देशक श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा हैं! थ्री इडियट्स, मुन्नाभाई एमबीबीएस, पीके, 1942 : ए लव स्टोरी जैसी फिल्मों के निर्माता रहे श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा ने लगभग 4 साल के कठोर परिश्रम से यह फ़िल्म बनाई है।

फ़िल्म में मनोज शर्मा की भूमिका प्रसिद्ध अभिनेता विक्रांत मैसी निभा रहे हैं। विकास सर की भूमिका में खुद विकास सर ही हैं!

यह इस फ़िल्म का टीज़र है। आप भी देखिये।

localized.title: 12th Fail Official Teaser | Vidhu Vinod Chopra | Vikrant Massey | 27th October 2023
localized.description:
प्रिय विद्यार्थी,

आपको ध्यान होगा कि करीब 4 साल पहले दृष्टि संस्थान के पूर्व विद्यार्थी मनोज कुमार शर्मा (IPS) के तैयारी के दिनों से जुड़े संघर्षों पर 'ट्वेल्थ फेल' नामक उपन्यास प्रकाशित हुआ था। इसमें दृष्टि की ही विद्यार्थी श्रद्धा जोशी (IRS) की कहानी भी थी जो मनोज की जीवनसंगिनी हैं। उपन्यास दृष्टि के ही पूर्व विद्यार्थी अनुराग पाठक (जॉइंट कमिश्नर, GST) ने लिखा था और भूमिका लिखी थी विकास सर ने!

अब इसी उपन्यास पर 27 अक्तूबर को एक बड़ी फिल्म आ रही है जिसके लेखक, निर्माता और निर्देशक श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा हैं! थ्री इडियट्स, मुन्नाभाई एमबीबीएस, पीके, 1942 : ए लव स्टोरी जैसी फिल्मों के निर्माता रहे श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा ने लगभग 4 साल के कठोर परिश्रम से यह फ़िल्म बनाई है।

फ़िल्म में मनोज शर्मा की भूमिका प्रसिद्ध अभिनेता विक्रांत मैसी निभा रहे हैं। विकास सर की भूमिका में खुद विकास सर ही हैं!

यह इस फ़िल्म का टीज़र है। आप भी देखिये।

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part -721 | Bhrigu Rishi Huye Bhargavi Ke Liye Chintit |  राधाकृष्ण #starbharat #radhakrishn 


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


#radhakrishn #starbharat #dildekedekhozara #mythology #राधाकृष्ण
#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

snippet.title: Gadar 2 का गदर प्रीमियर, बेटे Sunny Deol की फिल्म देखने पहुंचीं Prakash Kaur, Bobby बीवी के साथ आए
snippet.description:
सनी देओल की फिल्म गदर 2 सिनेमाघरों में गदर मचा रही है। तो ऐसा ही गदर बीती रात फिल्म के धमाकेदार प्रीमियर में भी नज़र आया । गदर 2 के रिलीज़ होते ही फिल्म के मेकर्स ने बीते दिन फिल्म का स्टारस्टडिड प्रीमियर होस्ट किया गया, जहां फिल्म को लेकर लोगों की दीवानगी और क्रेज़ साफ नज़र आया। 22 साल पाकिस्तान की बैंड बजाने तारा सिंह फिर दोबारा बॉर्डर पार पहुंचा है, तो तारा की दहाड़ सुनने बॉलीवुड भी खींचा चला आया।

#comedy2023 #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Iyer Ka Promotion https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3847 | 11 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3847: Gas Bich Mien Hui Khatam
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena assists Bhide in carrying the enormous basket of 40 kilograms of tomatoes inside the house, and Goli requests a tomato as a sign of thanks. Bhide cheerfully presents him with a plump red tomato as a symbol of appreciation. Madhvi is relieved that she can finally begin preparing her pickle for the order. Sonu and Bhide are munching on Madhvi's homemade "besan ladoos" when they hear Madhvi's voice. The father and daughter run to the kitchen to check on her and discover that a petrol cylinder needs to be fuelled this time. Bhide hurries to Sodhi's residence to acquire a replacement cylinder, but he uses a different firm. Is Madhvi going to be able to deliver the pickles on time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3847, 11 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: OMG 2 movie review | Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi, Yami Gautam | Honest Review
snippet.description:
OMG 2 is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language satirical comedy-drama film written and directed by Amit Rai. It is a spiritual sequel to OMG – Oh My God! (2012). The film stars Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi and Yami Gautam in lead roles, along with Pavan Malhotra, Govind Namdev, Arun Govil, Brijendra Kala and others. The film revolves around the subject of sex education in Indian schools. The film was theatrically released on 11 August 2023.

📝 Lyrics

(Payal Dev)

Baithi Baithi Mein Tune Aag Bhar Di 
Khali Bottle Mein Sharaab Bhar Di
Teri Kasam Bilkul Seedhi Sadi Thi Mein Tune Ladki Kharab Kar Di 

(Badshah)

Ya Ya 
Ek Baat Samajh Le 
Mein Bolu Kam Aankhon Se Padhle
Game Ke Top Pe Baitha 
Jiske Bhi Bas Ki Wo Aake Pakadle 
Inse Game Crack Hi Nai Hora.. Na 
Hit Koi Track Hi Nai Hora .. Na 
Yahaan Fir Maine Scene Change Kiya 
Aur Kuch Logo Ka Come Back Hi Nai Hora.. Woo
Badshah Hai Naam Meri Jaan, 
Pyaar So Mujhko Wo Baddie Bolti Hai, Aye
Game Mein Laundo Ka Baap Hoon Baby 
Ek Tu Hi Thodi Hai Jo Mujhe Daddy Bolti Hai

(Payal Dev)

Subah Se Shaam Tak, Bas Tera Naam Lu 
Tujhko Jo Dekhu Mein Dil Apna Thaam Lu
Jo Tu Mujhe Choole Toh Badan Mein Sansani
Khudko Samjhati Hu Ke Sabar Se Kaam Lu 
Neende Meri Tune Haraam Kar Di 
Gandi Meri Tune Zabaan Kar Di 
Teri Kasam Bilkul Seedhi Sadi Thi Mein Tune Ladki Kharab Kar Di 

(Badshah)

Koi Ungli Karta Hai, Haa, Toh Mein Baanh Bhi Chadhata Hu Par Saamne Ho Bandhi Toh Mein Good Boy Ban Jaata Hoon
Ya, Udti Hai Khabare Leta Na Stress, No
Game Ka Carter On To The Next, Ho
Plane Hai Private Life Hai Blessed, Yeah
Muthi Mein Game Mere Ghante Pe Press
Badboyshah Kaise Tuje Tere Bas Ka Laga 
Na Mujhe Aisa Maska Laga 
Rahi Na Kisi Kaam Dham Ki Jabse Ladki Ko Chaska Laga Mera

Ya , Ish You Boy , It’s Your Boy Badshah 

(Payal Dev) 

Ladki Kharab Kar Di

snippet.title: सबने क्यों  किया Bhide के लिए Clap? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Episode 334 | 9 August 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

As all the gents were having Soda at Abdul's shop, then suddenly Jethalal and all the other gents of the society were praising Bhide for getting the repair work of the society completed on time. Taarak was shocked to see Jethalal praising Bhide, but Bhide was also grateful in getting all the appreciation from his male friends. Now, Stay Tuned to know till when will there happiness last and what other exciting twists will change the scene of the situation.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 334
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: 'Chala Gaya WWE Se😢' Roman Reigns Bloodline Mystery, Jey Uso Quits WWE - WWE Smackdown Highlights
snippet.description:
Topics Covered In Video-
1) WWE Smackdown 11 August 2023 highlights & full show results in Hindi
2) Jey Uso quits WWE
3) Jey Uso said I am out of Smackdown, I am out of WWE
4) Jey Uso super kicks Jimmy Uso
5) Roman Reigns & The Bloodline on Smackdown
6) WWE Smackdown results

#smackdown #romanreigns #wwe 

'Chala Gaya WWE Se😢' Roman Reigns Bloodline Mystery, Jey Uso Quits WWE - WWE Smackdown Highlights

The WWE SmackDown highlights from the 11th of August 2023 showcased a captivating episode filled with intense action and emotional moments. In today's episode of WWE SmackDown, Roman Reigns took center stage, asserting his dominance as Universal Champion. The SmackDown highlights captured Roman Reigns' commanding presence, both in and out of the ring, as he continued to solidify his position at the top of WWE. Amidst the excitement, a shocking turn of events occurred as tensions within the Uso family escalated. Jey Uso's unexpected decision to quit WWE left fans stunned, and his subsequent attack on his brother Jimmy Uso, marked by a brutal superkick, added an emotional layer to the evening. The dynamic between Jey Uso and Roman Reigns was also on display, as their potential clash loomed in the spotlight. The SmackDown highlights provided a glimpse into the intricate storytelling that unfolded during the full show, leaving fans eagerly anticipating the next chapter in this gripping narrative
The match between Asuka and Charlotte Flair opens the event, with Flair posing confidently before the bell. Asuka charges, but Flair stands tall. They engage in a heated battle with counterattacks and signature moves. Flair gains the upper hand with powerful strikes and chops, but Asuka fights back with her fierce kicks. The action intensifies as Flair dominates, even delivering a top-rope maneuver. Asuka stages a comeback and gains control, prompting Damage CTRL – Bayley, Dakota Kai, and WWE Women’s Champion IYO SKY – to appear at ringside, causing a distraction.
Amid the chaos, Asuka capitalizes and nearly secures a victory, but the match ends in a no contest due to interference. Bayley targets Flair while SKY takes out Asuka with a missile dropkick. The celebration continues as SKY and Bayley proclaim their dominance, further establishing SKY as the new WWE Women’s Champion.
Later, AJ Styles faces off against Karrion Kross. The hard-hitting encounter sees both competitors trading offense, with Kross showcasing his power and aggression. However, AJ's resilience and athleticism shine through. Despite Scarlett's interference, AJ manages to secure the win with a Styles Clash, leading to a celebration with The O.C.
In another thrilling contest, Rey Mysterio challenges Austin Theory for the WWE United States Championship. Despite Theory's initial ambush on an injured Santos Escobar, the match is rebooked with Rey taking his place. Rey delivers his high-flying moves and counters, ultimately pinning Theory to become the new United States Champion. The LWO, including Santos Escobar, celebrates Rey's victory.
The event concludes with a tense family reunion as Jimmy Uso confronts his brother, Jey Uso, and Universal Champion Roman Reigns. Jimmy reveals that his actions at SummerSlam were motivated by his love for Jey and his fear of Jey becoming corrupted like Reigns. The emotional confrontation highlights the complex dynamics within The Bloodline stable, leaving the audience intrigued about the future of this storyline. Jey Uso superkick Roman Reigns, Solo Sikoa & Jimmy Uso. Jey Uso quits WWE saying I am out of WWE.

Amidst the excitement, a shocking turn of events occurred as tensions within the Uso family escalated. Jey Uso's unexpected decision to quit WWE left fans stunned, and his subsequent attack on his brother Jimmy Uso, marked by a brutal superkick, added an emotional layer to the evening. The dynamic between Jey Uso and Roman Reigns was also on display, as their potential clash loomed in the spotlight. The SmackDown highlights provided a glimpse into the intricate storytelling that unfolded during the full show, leaving fans eagerly anticipating the next chapter in this gripping narrative
The match between Asuka and Charlotte Flair opens the event, with Flair posing confidently before the bell. Asuka charges, but Flair stands tall. They engage in a heated battle with counterattacks and signature moves. Flair gains the upper hand with powerful strikes and chops, but Asuka fights back with her fierce kicks. The action intensifies as Flair dominates, even delivering a top-rope maneuver. Asuka stages a comeback and gains control, prompting Damage CTRL – Bayley, Dakota Kai, and WWE Women’s Champion IYO SKY – to appear at ringside, causing a distraction.
Amid the chaos, Asuka capitalizes and nearly secures a victory, but the match ends in a no contest due to interference. Bayley targets Flair while SKY takes out Asuka with a missile dropkick. The celebration continues as SKY and Bayley proclaim their dominance, further establishing SKY as the new WWE Women’s Champion.
Later, AJ Styles faces off against Karrion Kross. The hard-hitting encounter sees both competitors trading offense, with Kross showcasing his power and aggression. However, AJ's resilience and athleticism shine through. Despite Scarlett's interference, AJ manages to secure the win with a Styles Clash, leading to a celebration with The O.C.
In another thrilling contest, Rey Mysterio challenges Austin Theory for the WWE United States Championship. Despite Theory's initial ambush on an injured Santos Escobar, the match is rebooked with Rey taking his place. Rey delivers his high-flying moves and counters, ultimately pinning Theory to become the new United States Champion. The LWO, including Santos Escobar, celebrates Rey's victory.
The event concludes with a tense family reunion as Jimmy Uso confronts his brother, Jey Uso, and Universal Champion Roman Reigns. Jimmy reveals that his actions at SummerSlam were motivated by his love for Jey and his fear of Jey becoming corrupted like Reigns. The emotional confrontation highlights the complex dynamics within The Bloodline stable, leaving the audience intrigued about the future of this storyline. Jey Uso superkick Roman Reigns, Solo Sikoa & Jimmy Uso. Jey Uso quits WWE saying I am out of WWE.

snippet.title: Russia launches Luna-25 mission in race to sample moon's south pole
snippet.description:
A Soyuz-2 Fregat rocket carrying a lunar landing craft blasted off on what Russia hopes will be its first successful moon landing mission in nearly 50 years. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

The unmanned Luna-25's mission to the moon that is expected to take about five days and will seek to land near the south pole of the moon, collecting geological samples from the area. India’s Chandrayaan-3 space probe entered the moon’s orbit earlier this week, and will also explore the water-rich area near the south pole.

snippet.title: Thai Sticky Rice Recipe in Tamil | Sticky Rice with Mango | Dessert Recipes in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make thai sticky rice recipe in tamil. In this recipe I am going to compare making the recipe with thailand sticky rice as well as with our regular rice. The extra gluten in thai rice make is very stretchy and sticky once it is steamed. Sticky rice can be served in both sweet and savory recipes. The texture of the rice pairs well with other contrasting tastes and textures also the steamed rice has a mild sweetness to it.
#stickyricerecipe #mangostickyrice #thairecipe 

Friends, please do try this thai sticky rice recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part -719 | Shrinivas Aur Bhargavi Ki Bhent | राधाकृष्ण #starbharat #radhakrishn 


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


#radhakrishn #starbharat #dildekedekhozara #mythology #राधाकृष्ण
#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha
